WEBVTT

00:14.360 --> 00:15.040
Father

00:15.840 --> 00:16.760
Your son has lost

00:19.960 --> 00:21.360
Chess is like battle

00:21.880 --> 00:23.760
Never hesitate

00:24.440 --> 00:24.960
Remember

00:25.760 --> 00:26.960
Either don't compete

00:27.280 --> 00:28.040
Or compete

00:28.320 --> 00:29.520
To the very end

00:31.960 --> 00:32.560
Wen Xian

00:33.360 --> 00:34.520
You've been watching for a while

00:35.200 --> 00:35.960
Give your assessment

00:37.280 --> 00:39.240
Prince of Jin is quick-witted

00:39.480 --> 00:40.360
In chess, within the palace

00:40.360 --> 00:42.480
Only Your Majesty is his match

00:43.120 --> 00:44.360
Unlike Prince of Ning

00:44.480 --> 00:45.600
A terrible player

00:45.880 --> 00:47.280
Every time he gets something good

00:47.320 --> 00:49.440
He comes to the palace to gamble at chess with Your Majesty
